{"tid":56931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"辛巴威用小象　償還中國債務","createTime":"2016-12-27T15:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T17:53:04.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a5bbeb499391b3b22035eee93c6674ac9c99d38","tid":56931,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161227/640_30df573dec95e615a8deb1180387b6a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161227%2F640_30df573dec95e615a8deb1180387b6a2.jpg&h=9ead571e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161227/1021450/%E8%BE%9B%E5%B7%B4%E5%A8%81%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%80%E5%84%9F%E9%82%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20161227%2F1021450%2F%25E8%25BE%259B%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A8%2581%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2584%259F%25E9%2582%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2582%25B5%25E5%258B%2599&d=nbInO7Y79mucol7PE8Cah5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e44ca4af\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161227/1021450/%E8%BE%9B%E5%B7%B4%E5%A8%81%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%80%E5%84%9F%E9%82%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%99</a><br />\n<br />\n非洲國家辛巴威的動保人士向英國《泰晤士報》踢爆，辛巴威總統總統穆加比（Robert Mugabe）的51歲妻子格雷絲（Grace Mugabe）把35頭小象、8隻獅子、12隻狼及1隻長頸鹿送給中國一處動物園，用來償還欠下的軍服債務。<br />\n<br />\n辛巴威因購買用軍服和軍靴而欠債，據報這批動物經俄羅斯莫斯科空運到中國上海，再轉送到廣州的長隆野生動物世界。報導估計，一頭大象值4萬至6萬美元（約31萬至46.5萬港幣）。<br />\n<br />\n辛巴威的野生動物事務官員為生擒野生小象辯護，聲稱此舉可為國內野生動物公園減輕「過重」的負擔。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"86821b993e42d6b5dc5dd1955b80104ff6269ae9","tid":56931,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"兩個垃圾國家<br />\n世界災難"},{"pid":"a423b4fec146cf2ed9a0de3c1fdfea85b686ce63","tid":56931,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:45:01.000Z","msg":"大白象重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b513554900900512044a4950cf22aec0f08ed2","tid":56931,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T17:16:49.000Z","msg":"用動物黎做交易 佢地都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026c7439f9e341830ec2a10adafea874940ea74c","tid":56931,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T17:53:04.000Z","msg":"衫鞋都買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}